com.siperian.sif.message

Class TrustGraphData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.TrustGraphData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TrustGraphData
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents the data used to plot the trust decay curve for the specified trust setting.

    The data consists of two values: dates and trust values. These values are kept in separate arrays and can be retrieved by array index (see getDate(int) and getTrustValue(int)) or by the entire array (see getDates() and getTrustValues()).

    See Also:
    GetTrustGraphDataResponse, Serialized Form
